        CFI (cfiCond7) CFA_SP SP+6
        CFI (cfiCond7) CFA_Y Y+4
        CFI Block cfiCond8 Using cfiCommon0
        CFI (cfiCond8) NoFunction
        CFI (cfiCond8) Conditional ??CrossCallReturnLabel_6
        CFI (cfiCond8) R24 Frame(CFA_Y, -4)
